title.narrative: Kenya - Projet de ligne de transport d’électricité Mombasa-Nairobi
Kenya - The Mombasa-Nairobi Transmission Line Project

description.narrative: The objective of the project is to enhance the socio economic development of Kenya by reinforcing its transmission system and increasing the electricity access in the country. The project, when completed, will contribute towards reducing the power losses and increasing access of electricity in both rural and urban areas.
